{"tid":1737651,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"無啦啦比個家長屌","createTime":"2019-11-19T04:19:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T05:39:52.000Z","uid":256205,"like":228,"dislike":62,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"42e0c5305afe670c8e42aa6a112fe81a665c30cf","tid":1737651,"uid":256205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:19:00.000Z","msg":"屌個眼罩有窿我話應該唔係完全氣密咋喎<br />\n我冇撚嫌棄過任何一個你地比我嘅裝喎<br />\n你無啦啦屌柒我做乜鳩 起返我底<br />\n我成場運動都貫徹be humble呢個理念啊<br />\n我好聲好氣 你屌鳩我做乜撚嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你滷味我琴日就係尖東幫你地擋水炮<br />\n成個屎忽到小腿化學灼傷咁<br />\n有安全屋之後落街嘢飲都冇得買<br />\n拾荒咁周圍搵水飲<br />\n係彌敦道完全攻唔入poly <br />\n兩個大男人喊撚到傻咗<br />\n就係因為救唔到入面留守嘅手足<br />\n我竟然因為覺得一個眼罩唔氣密比人屌我浪費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我連塊包都慳住食喎屌你老母<br />\n原來我17年人生嘅尊嚴比唔上一個眼罩<br />\n<br />\n屌吖發夢發撚到醒返都嬲緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n少少負能量 sor9y"},{"pid":"2b2dc3860d42432ee024d6b59b9f895342b28299","tid":1737651,"uid":2419,"like":15,"dislike":8,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:20:23.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3f4faa5eb84bba474a27f8363cda59a817a11b4","tid":1737651,"uid":256205,"like":11,"dislike":5,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"2b2dc3860d42432ee024d6b59b9f895342b28299","tid":1737651,"uid":2419,"like":15,"dislike":8,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:20:23.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:21:13.000Z","msg":"晦氣說話啫 我作為一個冇乜樹窿嘅人 你唔好理我啦"},{"pid":"8ac1f93ebc16db56e5d2d6169f4409c13d3c9d77","tid":1737651,"uid":186844,"like":13,"dislike":41,"score":-28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T04:21:48.000Z","msg":"up乜9 咁就想做潮文？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb32bed41cb89521a3b1dc4fea95979b924cea3","tid":1737651,"uid":256205,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8ac1f93ebc16db